alle Tätigkeiten als UKG HRSD Implementierung Consultant auf englisch professionell beschrieben
ChatGPT:
Professional Responsibilities – UKG HR Service Delivery (HRSD) Implementation Consultant
Project Discovery & Scoping
Conduct end-to-end requirement workshops with HR, payroll, IT and compliance stakeholders; translate business needs into a signed Statement of Work and high-level solution design.
Functional Solution Design
Map current-state HR processes and design future-state workflows leveraging UKG HRSD modules (Case Management, Knowledge Base, Employee Files, Process Automation). Produce functional specifications and configuration workbooks.
System Configuration & Parametrisation
Configure service groups, security roles, data privacy settings, SLA matrices and escalation rules; build dynamic forms and routing logic using Studio and Process Designer.
Data Migration & Integration
Define ETL strategy, cleanse legacy data and execute bulk uploads via Data Loader. Design REST/SFTP integrations with core HCM (SAP SuccessFactors / Workday), payroll and identity-management systems.
Testing & Quality Assurance
Create test strategy and scripts (unit, SIT, UAT); lead defect triage cycles and ensure traceability against requirements. Automate regression tests where feasible.
Change Management & Training
Develop communication plan, stakeholder impact analyses and training curricula (train-the-trainer, e-learning videos, knowledge articles). Deliver live and virtual training sessions for HR agents and end users.
Go-Live & Hypercare
Orchestrate cut-over activities, monitor system health and SLA adherence, and manage hypercare support queues until transition to steady-state operations.
Continuous Improvement & Best Practices
Benchmark client KPIs, analyse ticket patterns and recommend automation opportunities (RPA, chatbots, Gen-AI knowledge search). Maintain reusable process templates and deployment accelerators.
Programme Governance
Report progress, risk and budget to steering committees; align with PMO governance frameworks (Prince2 Agile, Scrum). Coordinate vendors, near-shore teams and client resources across multiple time zones.
Pre-sales & Solution Advisory
Support RFP responses, deliver product demos and author effort estimates and business-case models highlighting ROI, compliance gains and employee-experience uplift.
These bullets can be pasted directly into the “Experience” section of your CV or LinkedIn profile under your UKG HRSD Consultant role.
