In my current projects I design case-management architectures that handle sensitive employee data for 20 000+ users. I gather requirements with C-level sponsors, map them in BPMN 2.0, build proof-of-concepts, run user-acceptance testing and own each go-live. Because compliance and data protection are non-negotiable, I work closely with security officers to align role models, encryption standards and audit trails – experience that will help me position and validate the PANW portfolio for customers who must protect their digital way of life.

