My background in agile and PRINCE2 governance lets me orchestrate specialist, services and customer-success teams as “one crew” – exactly how you describe the Solutions Consultant role.
Raised and educated in Germany, living in Switzerland, I am fluent in German and English and comfortable presenting to board-level audiences across EMEA. Remote and hybrid collaboration have been my daily routine for years, and I travel whenever a whiteboard session or on-site validation makes the difference.
