remotive.com
indeed.com
~ CHF 58 k – 160 k	Senior tracks (≥ $140 k) meet Zurich cost-of-living; boutique culture, fixed-price projects.
TopBloc – Workday Integrations Consultant (senior)	USA-wide remote	US $180 000 for senior IC role
ziprecruiter.com
~ CHF 160 k	Salary already on par with Swiss consulting houses, minus Swiss tax/social freight.
Gloat – Change & Transformation Consultant	Hybrid/remote US (fully-remote teams common)	US $120 000 – 150 000
theladders.com
indeed.com
~ CHF 107 k – 134 k	Talent-marketplace SaaS; pure advisory/change work with enterprise clients.
Alight / Strada – HR Transformation Consultant (global HR-tech consultancy)	UK & Ireland – advertised fully remote	Band not disclosed, but Glassdoor/Gartner surveys put senior HR-transf. consultants at £70 k – £95 k (≈ CHF 82 k – 112 k)	Good for CH if billed in GBP + bonus; travel low, benefits solid.
builtin.com
*Published by the employer or salary tracker in the posting; excludes bonus/equity.
Why these numbers matter for Switzerland
Cost baseline: A single consultant in the greater-Zurich area typically needs ~ CHF 85 k– 95 k gross to match the Swiss median standard of living (health-care, 2-room flat, retirement contributions).
Net parity: US-denominated packages ≥ US $130 k (≈ CHF 115 k) still leave head-room after Swiss social security (AHV, PK) if you invoice through a Swiss GmbH or take an „employer of record“.
Equity & bonus: Workday, TopBloc and Gloat top their cash with RSUs or annual bonuses (often 10–15 %), giving an extra cushion against FX swings.
How to unearth (and win) these roles
Target the SaaS partner network
Boutiques like TopBloc, Invisors, Collaborative Solutions, Cognizant, Kainos all run fully-remote project teams and publish salary bands in the US market.
Use geo-agnostic boards with salary filters
LinkedIn → “Remote”, “HR Transformation Consultant”, filter “$120 000 +” (works globally).
Remotive / Himalayas / DailyRemote index US-based consulting jobs with disclosed ranges.
Tap EMEA advisory practices
Alight (Strada), Mercer Digital, PwC People & Org, EY PAS increasingly hire “virtual first” consultants across Europe—advertised in GBP/EUR but negotiable in CHF for Swiss contractors.
Negotiate smart
Convert target CHF net → gross USD/GBP (add 8–10 % FX buffer).
Ask for contractor uplift (≈ 10–15 %) to cover your Swiss social charges.
Separate travel days and on-call SLAs so remote stays remote.
Bottom line: fully remote HR-Digital-Transformation consulting roles do exist at global and boutique consultancies, with cash ranges of CHF 110 k – 160 k+—well within the level you’re used to from Swiss on-site gigs, only without the commute. Start with the Workday and TopBloc postings for immediate openings, keep Alight/Strada on the radar for EMEA-centric work, and set LinkedIn salary alerts at 120 k USD/GBP to catch the next wave.
